    "title": "京东开放平台商品发布规避信息细则",
    "followRuleId": "1268089757632696320",
    "content": "<h1 style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1.</span></strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">【违规定义】</span></strong></h1>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1.1</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">更换商品：指商家在已有商品（<span style=\"background-color: #ecf0f1;\">SKU</span>）链接上将原商品更换为另一款商品进行销售的行为，更换后的商品在类目、品牌、颜色、型号、品种等属性上发生了改变。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1.2</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">图片利用视觉效果隐藏关键信息导致用户误解：指商家通过修改字体/图案大小、色彩等，导致从视觉上完全改变整体含义并产生消费者误解的行为。</span></p>\n<h1 style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2.</span></strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">【处理措施】</span></strong></h1>\n<h2 style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2.1</span></strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">更换商品：</span></strong></h2>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 3; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2.1.1&nbsp;</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">违规程度一般：<span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000;\">扣除违约金200元（M2）；</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 3; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2.1.2&nbsp;</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">违规程度严重：<span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\">扣除违约金500元（M2），违规商品搜索、推荐降权（降权比例基于严重程度25%-100%不等）；</span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 3; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2.1.3&nbsp;</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">违规程度极其严重：<span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\">扣除违约金800元（M2），违规商品搜索、推荐屏蔽；</span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 3; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2.1.4&nbsp;</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">除上述处理措施外，如商家多次出现违规行为或因上述行为引起重大投诉的，京东有权视违规行为对商家采取包括但不限于违规商品下架或修改（商品信息修改）、店铺屏蔽、全店下架、限制使用咚咚、扣除违约金、冻结资金、加收风险保证金、清退等处理措施。</span></p>\n<h2 style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2.2</span></strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">图片利用视觉效果隐藏关键信息导致用户误解：</span></strong></h2>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 3; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2.2.1&nbsp;</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">违规程度一般：警告；</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 3; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2.2.2&nbsp;</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">违规程度严重：预警整改，超期未整改或整改失败下架违规商品；</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 3; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2.2.3&nbsp;</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">违规程度极其严重：下架违规商品、并扣除违约金最低500元；</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 3; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2.2.4&nbsp;</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">除上述处理措施外，如商家多次出现违规行为或因上述行为引起重大投诉的，京东有权视违规行为对商家采取包括但不限于违规商品下架或修改（商品信息修改）、店铺屏蔽、全店下架、限制使用咚咚、扣除违约金、冻结资金、加收风险保证金、清退等处理措施。</span></p>\n<h1 style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3.</span></strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">【规则解读】</span></strong></h1>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 3; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3.1&nbsp;</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">平台根据违规行为对用户体验造成的伤害程度，从轻到重执行M1到M7档位违约金，具体金额如下：</span></span></p>\n<table style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; border-collapse: collapse; max-width: 100%; word-break: break-all; color: #000000; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 3;\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\">\n<tr style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\">\n<td style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px; padding: 0.75pt; font-size: 14px; text-align: left; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; width: 60pt; background-color: #e5e6e9;\" width=\"80\">\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">档位</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px; padding: 0.75pt; font-size: 14px; text-align: left; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; width: 104.4pt; background-color: #e5e6e9;\" width=\"139\">\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">用户体验伤害分级</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px; padding: 0.75pt; font-size: 14px; text-align: left; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; width: 319.8pt; background-color: #e5e6e9;\" width=\"426\">\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">违约金标准</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\">\n<td style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px; padding: 0.75pt; font-size: 14px; text-align: left; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; width: 60pt;\" width=\"80\">\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; line-height: 28px; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, s